{"title":"白雪吟——与友人同题诗","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":12,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白雪吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——与友人同题诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道雪落无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落有声，极轻，极轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“惟独圣洁的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能听清。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落有声，很轻，很轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对心灵撞击却很重，很重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那圣洁的精灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让多少人怦然心动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿童听雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听出童年风景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农听雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听丰收锣鼓声声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是诗人多情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听，口咏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗吟道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万里江山净化中……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悟雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落无声胜有声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少话，尽在不言中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看人的悟性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女悟的是纯情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人悟的是空灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问君："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你悟出何情何境？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏雪访友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏雪寻梅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种诗的韵味。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让脚印真真切切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里一定无愧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小偷敢头一个踏雪吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今中外只有它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才称得上玉骨冰肌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走时，无踪无迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不生烟，也不占地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪中留影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与白留影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与洁合影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如幻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如梦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人走了，南北西东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪化了，入地无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是匆匆过客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下永恒风景。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}